Complete Pack: Although compact and lightweight, this vehicle first aid kit truly has everything you need. You get a total of 230 accessories, including a wide range of bandages, silicone tourniquet, adhesive wound dressing, sterile swabs, foil blanket, CPR mask, gloves, sterile eye pads, tweezers, scissors, whistle, saber cards, adhesive tape, and safety pins.
Practical and Easy to Store: This first aid kit home comes with a compact and lightweight EVA hardcase that is very easy to store. The case is also waterproof and durable for more practicality.

Universal Use: This waterproof first aid kit is a great option for virtually any situation. Keep this first aid kit in your car, boat, home, office, school, or take it with you when camping or hiking to make sure you are prepared in case of an emergency.

Multipurpose Design: Whether it’s just a minor accident that leads to a superficial wound or something serious such as earthquakes, accidents, or falls that can lead to terrible injuries, our emergency boat kit can prove of great help until specialized medical care arrives.
body.description: CureIT is a brand that puts your safety and happiness above all else. You know how important it is to be prepared in case of an emergency. That’s why we have designed a premium first aid kit featuring 230 different accessories that allow you to take care of minor wounds and keep yourself or others safe at least until specialized medical care arrives. This first aid kit home is a practical and easy way to make sure you are always ready in case of an emergency. What makes this product special? Our first aid kit waterproof features everything you need to take care of superficial wounds, including burns, cuts, scratches, blisters, rashes, and many others. We have included in the home first aid kit family box not just a wide range of bandages but also various supplies (swabs, eye pads, emergency foil blanket), tools such as tweezers, scissors, and a whistle. Some features to keep in mind about our product: Complete 230pcs first aid kit; Waterproof case; EVA hard case design; Ideal for cars, homes, boats, schools, offices; Lightweight and compact; Easy to store and carry; Great for outdoor hiking and camping; Suitable in case of emergencies; Smooth surface; Easy to clean; Practical and intuitive accessories. Keep yourself and your family safe with the help of our practical first aid kit!
